<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 09:13:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国选手李勇夺男子25m手枪速射金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/shooting-chinas-li-wins-gold-mens-25m-rapid-fire-pistol-2024-08-05/</link><description>周一，中国选手李跃红在巴黎奥运会男子25米手枪速射比赛中获得金牌，韩国选手曹英宰获得银牌，中国选手王新杰获得铜牌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 08:15:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/shooting-chinas-li-wins-gold-mens-25m-rapid-fire-pistol-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>监测组织称，中国无人驾驶军机在越南海岸附近被追踪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/uncrewed-chinese-military-aircraft-tracked-close-vietnam-coast-monitor-group-2024-08-05/</link><description>南海研究机构告诉路透社，上周，一架打开跟踪器的中国军用无人驾驶飞机在越南海岸附近飞行，这是该组织五年来的监测中，北京首次公开此类行动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 08:02:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/uncrewed-chinese-military-aircraft-tracked-close-vietnam-coast-monitor-group-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>缅甸军政府称叛乱分子占领主要基地后高级军官被扣押</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-junta-says-senior-officers-held-rebels-take-over-major-base-2024-08-05/</link><description>缅甸军政府与中国边境附近一个主要军事基地的高级官员失去了联系，这是在叛军宣布控制了重要的地区军队总部后罕见地承认战场失败。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 07:44:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-junta-says-senior-officers-held-rebels-take-over-major-base-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国要求大型国有金融机构放弃审计师普华永道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-asks-large-state-financial-institutions-drop-auditor-pwc-say-sources-2024-08-05/</link><description>两位消息人士称，近几个月来，中国监管机构已要求普华永道 (PwC) 的几家大型国有客户放弃该审计师，因为该审计师准备因其为陷入困境的房地产开发商恒大集团所做的工作而受到处罚。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 07:34:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-asks-large-state-financial-institutions-drop-auditor-pwc-say-sources-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>美军着眼澳大利亚印度洋脚趾以威慑中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-military-eyes-australias-indian-ocean-toe-hold-deter-china-2024-08-05/</link><description>澳大利亚一个偏远岛屿靠近中国石油运输的印度洋咽喉要道，该岛被列入美国可能进行军事建设的地点清单，旨在威慑中国，美国表示该岛“可能会也可能不会”支持美国军队。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 07:15:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-military-eyes-australias-indian-ocean-toe-hold-deter-china-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，中国结婚夫妇数量降至12年来最低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/number-chinese-couples-getting-married-falls-12-year-low-data-shows-2024-08-05/</link><description>官方数据显示，由于经济放缓和生活成本上升，越来越多的年轻人推迟结婚，今年上半年中国结婚人数降至2013年以来的最低水平。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 05:52:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/number-chinese-couples-getting-married-falls-12-year-low-data-shows-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>金价创历史新高可能会抑制需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/golds-run-record-high-may-crimp-demand-russell-2024-08-05/</link><description>今年迄今为止，黄金一直是表现出色的大宗商品，上涨了 18.5%，创下历史新高。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 05:30:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/golds-run-record-high-may-crimp-demand-russell-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>由于回收利润下降，Aurubis 第三季度盈利预期不及预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/aurubis-q3-earnings-miss-expectations-recycling-revenue-falls-2024-08-05/</link><description>欧洲最大的铜生产商 Aurubis 周一公布的第三季度税前利润 (EBT) 低于预期，受到回收利润下降和硫酸价格的拖累。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 05:23:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/aurubis-q3-earnings-miss-expectations-recycling-revenue-falls-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国荣耀在准备首次公开募股时获得了“异常”强大的国家支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-honor-gets-strong-state-backing-it-readies-ipo-2024-08-05/</link><description>据政策文件和知情人士透露，随着前华为 (HWT.UL) 子公司准备首次公开募股 (IPO)，中国智能手机制造商荣耀正获得当地政府支持者“不同寻常”的高水平支持。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 05:15:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-honor-gets-strong-state-backing-it-readies-ipo-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾和越南将举行首次海岸警卫队联合演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-vietnam-hold-first-ever-joint-coast-guard-exercise-2024-08-05/</link><description>菲律宾和越南将于本周在马尼拉湾启动首次联合海岸警卫队演习，这符合两国加强海上合作的承诺。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 04:50:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-vietnam-hold-first-ever-joint-coast-guard-exercise-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>晨标：沐浴在红色的海洋中</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-05/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 04:33:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>投资者对全球股市暴跌的评论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-selloff-quotes-2024-08-05/</link><description>周一，全球股市暴跌，债券上涨，原因是对美国可能陷入衰退的担忧导致投资者纷纷逃离风险资产，同时押注利率必须迅速下降才能挽救经济增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 03:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-selloff-quotes-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国东部创纪录气温，电力需求激增</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/high-temperatures-scorch-china-spiking-power-demand-2024-08-05/</link><description>中国东部地区遭遇反常高温，预计江苏和浙江等高度工业化省份的沿海大城市将持续长达10天的高温。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 02:26:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/high-temperatures-scorch-china-spiking-power-demand-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示中国服务业活动进一步扩张，但外部需求放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-services-activity-expands-further-external-demand-slows-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-08-05/</link><description>周一的一项私营部门调查显示，尽管海外需求势头放缓至 11 个月来的最低水平，但在新订单的推动下，7 月份中国服务业活动加速增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:51:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-services-activity-expands-further-external-demand-slows-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大电动汽车子公司进入破产重组程序</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-evergrandes-ev-arm-units-enter-bankruptcy-reorganization-proceedings-2024-08-05/</link><description>中国恒大新能源汽车周一表示，在该公司的两个子公司的个人债权人提出破产程序一周后，当地法院已裁定该公司的两个子公司应进入破产并进行重组。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:24:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-evergrandes-ev-arm-units-enter-bankruptcy-reorganization-proceedings-2024-08-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>